Note:
This file handles core HIR (High-level Intermediate Representation) type definitions and data structures.

This file performs the following tasks:
- Process core HIR type definitions and HIR data structure management
- Handle HIR expression types and HIR statement types
- Manage HIR declaration types and HIR metadata types
- Process HIR type system and HIR semantic information

This file is essential because of the following reasons:
- Core HIR types enable high-level semantic representation
- Proper HIR type handling ensures correct HIR data structure management
- Core HIR types support enables Runa compilation for semantic analysis

This file consists of the following functions/features/operation types:
- Core HIR type definitions and HIR data structure management
- HIR expression types and HIR statement types
- HIR declaration types and HIR metadata types
- HIR type system and HIR semantic information

Dependencies:
- Imports AST types from frontend for conversion
- Imports memory/layout.runa for structure allocation
- Imports collections/list.runa for child node management
- Imports core/string_core.runa for string operations
:End Note

Import "compiler/frontend/parsing/ast.runa" as AST
Import "compiler/frontend/primitives/memory/layout.runa" as Layout
Import "compiler/frontend/primitives/collections/list.runa" as List
Import "compiler/frontend/primitives/core/string_core.runa" as StringCore

